		<h2>Titel:</h2><div class="t"><div class="b"><div class="l"><div class="r"><div class="bl"><div class="br"><div class="tl"><div class="tr">Königin von Kastilien und L&eacute;on<br /><br />Titularkönigin von Arag&oacute;n, Mallorca, Neapel und Valencia</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
		<h2>Zivilisation:</h2><div class="t"><div class="b"><div class="l"><div class="r"><div class="bl"><div class="br"><div class="tl"><div class="tr"><a href="CIVILIZATION_SPAIN.aspx" onmouseover="return tooltip('Spanisches Reich');" onmouseout="return hideTip();"><img src="/civilopedia/images/small/CIVILIZATION_SPAIN.png" /></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
